{"tid":2350542,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"今次疫症算唔算終於到四眼仔發圍","createTime":"2021-01-02T11:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T13:42:34.000Z","uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0f0fbf628c44a51635a0f4c0dfb9a11719809031","tid":2350542,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T11:42:53.000Z","msg":"疫症撗行，每個人都迫住要戴口罩生活，<br />\n但係戴口罩有個難題，就係啲口罩戴得耐就會好易鬆，<br />\n根據風動力學指出冷空氣向下沉，而熱空氣就係向上升，<br />\n咁啲霧氣就會由個鼻噴上去，搞到啲人個視野俾霧氣擋住睇唔得清，<br />\n而做四眼仔有個好處，就係副眼鏡個鼻托可以襟實個口罩上方，<br />\n咁啲霧氣就唔會谷到上去整到個人迷失方向咁款。"},{"pid":"eb719826a6c5b181b850f3dc0e80606bd5c04266","tid":2350542,"uid":184233,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T11:43:50.000Z","msg":"1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e888c366eeaf5719219482f9a5a2b07b168c5dee","tid":2350542,"uid":58880,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T11:44:32.000Z","msg":"On9 噴氣個陣咪遮到眼鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b545aea49d985e2215c6cd53d54527ebd0f5c7b3","tid":2350542,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T11:45:14.000Z","msg":"ON LUN 9"},{"pid":"6e2acffaf3919632cac695204a83319f377743bb","tid":2350542,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T11:45:30.000Z","msg":"？？？？"},{"pid":"8954bcba2afb66f5cc051a8a9156a879821645be","tid":2350542,"uid":277578,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:08:33.000Z","msg":"講嘢一舊舊。十足死老豆。"},{"pid":"9dfa4eeb508fc62e4e0dcc376eef6b77fe9aa3c6","tid":2350542,"uid":56550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:17:24.000Z","msg":"傻人發現案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66aac82f7452477d9634695548dcbc0b5bce4ed9","tid":2350542,"uid":373442,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:54:19.000Z","msg":"冇眼鏡點會有霧氣<img src=\"/assets/